You can't come back!

38
00:05:50,433 --> 00:05:53,769
It's back.
The Popeil Pocket Fisherman.

39
00:05:53,936 --> 00:05:55,854
Take my husband, take my kids...

40
00:05:56,022 --> 00:05:59,024
- Are you all right?
- Hmm?

41
00:05:59,192 --> 00:06:01,693
