223
00:23:16,186 --> 00:23:19,730
Now, I'm sure you
had reason, Paul...

224
00:23:19,940 --> 00:23:23,734
...but like it or not, the wife
of the governor has only one nephew...

225
00:23:23,944 --> 00:23:25,820
...and his name
is Percy Wetmore.

226
00:23:26,029 --> 00:23:27,947
